scores.winnerSurface:
Extract the transaction info from the message as JSON.
Example: {"merchant": "Starbucks", "amount": 5.75, "date": "2023-10-05", "category": "dining"}
 Use keys: merchant, amount, date, category. Amount must be a bare number. Date must be ISO YYYY-MM-DD. Category must be one of: groceries, dining, transport, utilities, entertainment.
